quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  62,1,jo cheez asmano mein hai aur jo cheez zameen mein hai sab khuda ki tasbeeh karti hai jo badshah haqeeqi pak zaat zabardast hikmat wala hai
  62,2,wohi to hai jis ne un parhon mein un hi mein se ( Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) ko paighambar ( bana kar ) bheja jo un ke samnay is ki ayatain parhte aur un ko pak karte aur ( khuda ki ) kitaab aur danai sikhate hain. aur is y pehlay to yeh log Sarih gumraahi mein they
  62,3,aur un mein se aur logon ki taraf bhi ( un ko bheja hai ) jo abhi un ( musalmanoon se ) nahi miley. aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  62,4,yeh khuda ka fazl hai jisay chahta hai ataa karta hai. aur khuda barray fazl ka maalik hai
  62,5,jin logon ( ke sir ) par torat ladwai gayi phir unhon ne is ( ke baar tameel ) ko nah uthaya un ki misaal gadhay ki si hai jin par barri barri kitaaben ldi hon. jo log khuda ki aayton ki takzieeb karte hain un ki misaal buri hai. aur khuda zalim logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
  62,6,keh do ke ae yahood agar tum ko daawa ho ke tum hi khuda ke dost ho aur log nahi to agar tum sachey ho to ( zara ) mout ki arzoo to karo
  62,7,aur yeh un ( aamaal ) ke sabab jo kar chukay hain hargiz is ki arzoo nahi karen ge. aur khuda zaalmon se khoob waaqif hai
  62,8,keh do ke mout jis se tum guraiz karte ho woh to tumahray samnay aa kar rahay gi. phir tum posheeda aur zahir ke jan-nay walay ( khuda ) ki taraf lout’tay jao ge phir jo kuch tum karte rahay ho woh sab tumhe betaye ga
